<table class="summaryTable">
<tr><td colspan="3">
<div class="signature2">
public void <b>setDriverName</b>(string $driverName)</div>
</td></tr>
<tr>
  <td class="paramNameCol">$driverName</td>
  <td class="paramTypeCol">string</td>
  <td class="paramDescCol">to be set. Valid values are the keys from the <a href="/doc/api/1.1/CDbConnection#driverMap">driverMap</a> property.</td>
</tr>
</table>

<div class="sourceCode">
<b>Source Code:</b> <a class="sourceLink" href="https://github.com/yiisoft/yii/blob/1.1.16/framework/db/CDbConnection.php#L726">framework/db/CDbConnection.php#726</a> (<b><a href="#" class="show">show</a></b>)
<div class="code"><code><span style="color: #000000">
<span style="color: #0000BB"></span><span style="color: #007700">public&nbsp;function&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">setDriverName</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$driverName</span><span style="color: #007700">)<br />{<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$this</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">_driverName</span><span style="color: #007700">=</span><span style="color: #0000BB">strtolower</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$driverName</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />}</span>
</span>
</code></div>
</div>
<p>Changes the name of the DB driver. Overrides value extracted from the <a href="/doc/api/1.1/CDbConnection#connectionString">connectionString</a>,
which is behavior by default.</p>

